title.narrative: Lao PDR Customs and Trade Facilitation Project

description.narrative: The objective of the project is to facilitate trade by improving the efficiency and effectiveness of customs administration and simplifying customs procedures to eliminate duplication and redundancy, reduce transactions costs and time to clear goods, and increasetransparencyand accountability.
